# ┗━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┛

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Typography (font-family set in platform-specific configs)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
font-style-bold = Bold
font-style-italic = Italic
font-style-bold-italic = Bold Italic
font-size = 14
font-thicken = true
adjust-cell-height = 10%
adjust-cursor-thickness = 2

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Window & Transparency
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
background-opacity = 0.85
background-blur-radius = 20
window-padding-x = 14
window-padding-y = 10
window-padding-balance = true
window-padding-color = extend
window-decoration = true
macos-titlebar-style = tabs
window-theme = dark
window-colorspace = display-p3
window-vsync = true
window-save-state = always
window-inherit-working-directory = true
window-inherit-font-size = true

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Theme — SilkCircuit Neon (from ~/.config/ghostty/themes/)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
theme = silkcircuit-neon
minimum-contrast = 1.1

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Cursor
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
cursor-style = block
cursor-style-blink = true
cursor-opacity = 0.9
cursor-click-to-move = true

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Splits & Focus
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
unfocused-split-opacity = 0.80
focus-follows-mouse = true

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Mouse & Interactions
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
mouse-hide-while-typing = true
mouse-scroll-multiplier = 3

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Clipboard & Selection
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
copy-on-select = clipboard
clipboard-read = allow
clipboard-write = allow
clipboard-trim-trailing-spaces = true
clipboard-paste-protection = true
clipboard-paste-bracketed-safe = true

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Hyperlinks & URLs
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
link-url = true

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Shell Integration
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
shell-integration = detect
shell-integration-features = cursor,sudo,title,no-ssh-terminfo

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Scrollback & Performance (50MB buffer)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
scrollback-limit = 50000000

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Quick Terminal — Drop-down quake style
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
quick-terminal-position = top
quick-terminal-screen = mouse
quick-terminal-animation-duration = 0.15
quick-terminal-autohide = true

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Resize Overlay
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
resize-overlay = after-first
resize-overlay-position = bottom-right
resize-overlay-duration = 500ms

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# macOS Refinements
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
macos-option-as-alt = true
confirm-close-surface = false
quit-after-last-window-closed = false
window-step-resize = true

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Keybindings — SilkCircuit workflow essentials
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Tabs
keybind = super+t=new_tab
keybind = super+w=close_surface
keybind = super+shift+]=next_tab
keybind = super+shift+[=previous_tab

# Splits
keybind = super+d=new_split:right
keybind = super+shift+d=new_split:down
keybind = super+alt+left=goto_split:left
keybind = super+alt+right=goto_split:right
keybind = super+alt+up=goto_split:top
keybind = super+alt+down=goto_split:bottom
keybind = super+ctrl+left=resize_split:left,20
keybind = super+ctrl+right=resize_split:right,20
keybind = super+ctrl+up=resize_split:up,20
keybind = super+ctrl+down=resize_split:down,20
# keybind = super+shift+enter=equalize_splits  # Commented for Claude Code shift+enter

# Font scaling
keybind = super+equal=increase_font_size:1
keybind = super+minus=decrease_font_size:1
keybind = super+0=reset_font_size

# Utilities
keybind = super+k=clear_screen
keybind = super+shift+c=copy_to_clipboard
keybind = super+shift+v=paste_from_clipboard

# Quick terminal toggle (global hotkey)
keybind = global:ctrl+grave_accent=toggle_quick_terminal

# Shift+Enter for multiline input (escape + carriage return)
keybind = shift+enter=text:\x1b\r

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Auto updates
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
auto-update-channel = tip

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Platform-specific configs (fonts, etc.)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
config-file = ?macos.conf
config-file = ?linux.conf
config-file = ?hyperia.conf
config-file = ?auto/theme.ghostty
